item.title: Beam Column Joint
item.description: source The example files (PR.tcl, procMKPC2.tcl, procUniaxialPinching.tcl, procRC2.tcl) create a model of a RC beam column sub-assemblage. The cruciform is subjected to constant gravity load at nodes 4 and 7 and pseudo-static cyclic lateral load under displacement control at node 10.
